    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A colorless, volatile, extremely flammable liquid, miscible with water; obtained as a byproduct of wood distillation or the fermentation of corn mash. Used as a solvent, cleaning fluid, fuel additive, and for dyeing cotton, among other uses.</Note_Text>
